column1:
Such an honour for me to be a learner at Microsoft Indonesia for Cloud Fundamental by MSIB Kampus Merdeka of Ministry of Education, Culture, Research and Technology Indonesia. I did 2 sessions, synchronous and asynchronous sessions. The synchronous activity was held with my mentor in class CF004 Erick Kurniawan who explained some focuses on Azure Fundamentals, Microsoft Certified: Security, Compliance, and Identity Fundamentals, Power Platform Fundamentals, and Microsoft Azure Administrator. For the synchronous activities, I worked for the learning path on the Microsoft Team. As an electrical engineering student, this study is a very new thing for me. I gained new knowledge from the discussions and explanations. Such a very pleasant experience for me to be able to join with students who have high curiosity and learn new things that I have never tried before. 

